'''硫化鍶'''，化學式為SrS，是一种白色固体。硫化锶是把重要的锶矿[[天青石|天青石]]（硫酸锶）转换成其它锶化合物的中间体。<ref name=Ullmann>J. Paul MacMillan, Jai Won Park, Rolf Gerstenberg, Heinz Wagner, Karl Köhler, Peter Wallbrecht  “Strontium and Strontium Compounds” in Ullmann's Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry 2002, Wiley-VCH, Weinheim. {{DOI|10.1002/14356007.a25_321}}.</ref><ref name=Celestine>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mindat.org/min-927.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-06-26 |archive-date=2021-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211020002707/https://www.mindat.org/min-927.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=IMA>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ima-mineralogy.org/Minlist.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-06-26 |archive-date=2021-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211220223545/https://www.ima-mineralogy.org/Minlist.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>因其點燃是有亮紅色火焰而用作[[煙火|煙火]]的添加劑，也可用於[[脫毛|脫毛]]<ref name="Robert E. Krebs">{{cite book| author= Robert E. Krebs | title= The History And Use of Our Earth's Chemical Elements: A Reference Guide | url= https://archive.org/details/historyuseofoure0000kreb | publisher= Greenwood Publishing Group | ISBN = 031333438-2 | date= 2006 |page = [https://archive.org/details/historyuseofoure0000kreb/page/n105 78] }}</ref>和夜光[[塗料|塗料]]的熒光粉。 

== 製備 ==
硫化锶可以由天青石和[[焦炭|焦炭]]在 110–1300 °C下反应而成。<ref name=hydrometallurgy>{{cite journal |journal= Hydrometallurgy |volume= 84 |issue= 3–4 |year= 2006 |pages= 239–246 |title= Dissolution kinetics of celestite (SrSO<sub>4</sub>) in HCl solution with BaCl<sub>2</sub> |first1= Salih |last1= Aydoğan |first2= Murat |last2= Erdemoğlu |first3= Ali |last3= Aras |first4= Gökhan |last4= Uçar |first5= Alper |last5= Özkan |doi= 10.1016/j.hydromet.2006.06.001 }}</ref> 其中，天青石的硫酸根被[[还原|还原]]成硫离子：
:SrSO<sub>4</sub>  + 2 C   →   SrS  +  2 CO<sub>2</sub>
每年约有 300,000 吨的硫化锶这样被制造。<ref name=Ullmann/>

硫化鍶可通過硫和锶直接在惰性气氛中反应而成：<ref name="Richard C. Ropp">{{cite book| author= Richard C. Ropp | title= Encyclopedia of the Alkaline Earth Compounds | publisher= Newnes | ISBN = 044459553-8 | date= 2012 | page = 140 }}</ref>
:<math>\mathrm{Sr + S \rightarrow SrS}</math>

它也可以由[[碳酸锶|碳酸锶]]在 1000 °C 和[[硫化氢|硫化氢]]蒸汽反应而成。<ref name="brauer">[[Georg_Brauer|Georg Brauer]] (Hrsg.), unter Mitarbeit von [[Marianne_Baudler|Marianne Baudler]] u. a.: ''Handbuch der Präparativen Anorganischen Chemie.'' 3., umgearbeitete Auflage. Band II, Ferdinand Enke, Stuttgart 1978, ISBN 3-432-87813-3, S. 927.</ref>

